{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":724,"text":"If there's any power in design,"},{"time":3428,"text":"that's the power of synthesis."},{"time":5771,"text":"The more complex the problem,"},{"time":7466,"text":"the more the need for simplicity."},{"time":9967,"text":"So allow me to share three cases"},{"time":12304,"text":"where we tried to apply"},{"time":14114,"text":"design's power of synthesis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17117,"text":"Let's start with the global challenge of urbanization."},{"time":21218,"text":"It's a fact that people are moving towards cities."},{"time":24896,"text":"and even if counterintuitive, it's good news."},{"time":28361,"text":"Evidence shows that people are better off in cities."},{"time":32444,"text":"But there's a problem that I would call"},{"time":34593,"text":"the \"3S\" menace:"},{"time":36899,"text":"The scale, speed, and scarcity of means"},{"time":39632,"text":"with which we will have to\nrespond to this phenomenon"},{"time":42827,"text":"has no precedence in history."},{"time":45465,"text":"For you to have an idea,"},{"time":46654,"text":"out of the three billion \npeople living in cities today,"},{"time":49880,"text":"one billion are under the line of poverty."},{"time":53271,"text":"By 2030, out of the five billion people"},{"time":57210,"text":"that will be living in cities,"},{"time":59480,"text":"two billion are going to \nbe under the line of poverty."},{"time":62837,"text":"That means that we will have to build"},{"time":69605,"text":"a one million-person city per week"},{"time":78114,"text":"with 10,000 dollars per family"},{"time":83672,"text":"during the next 15 years."},{"time":85482,"text":"A one million-person city per week"},{"time":88206,"text":"with 10,000 dollars per family."},{"time":90330,"text":"If we don't solve this equation,"},{"time":91995,"text":"it is not that people \nwill stop coming to cities."},{"time":94043,"text":"They will come anyhow,"},{"time":95952,"text":"but they will live in slums, favelas"},{"time":98958,"text":"and informal settlements."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100368,"text":"So what to do? Well, an answer may come"},{"time":103246,"text":"from favelas and slums themselves."},{"time":107840,"text":"A clue could be in this \nquestion we were asked"},{"time":111433,"text":"10 years ago."},{"time":112890,"text":"We were asked to accommodate 100 families"},{"time":116521,"text":"that had been occupying illegally"},{"time":118939,"text":"half a hectare in the center"},{"time":121234,"text":"of the city of Iquique \nin the north of Chile"},{"time":124134,"text":"using a $10,000 subsidy"},{"time":127062,"text":"with which we had to buy the land,"},{"time":130176,"text":"provide the infrastructure,"},{"time":131909,"text":"and build the houses that, \nin the best of the cases,"},{"time":135230,"text":"would be of around 40 square meters."},{"time":138894,"text":"And by the way, they said,"},{"time":141099,"text":"the cost of the land,"},{"time":142750,"text":"because it's in the center of the city,"},{"time":144806,"text":"is three times more"},{"time":146550,"text":"than what social housing can normally afford."},{"time":150108,"text":"Due to the difficulty of the question,"},{"time":152334,"text":"we decided to include the families"},{"time":154516,"text":"in the process of understanding the constraints,"},{"time":158612,"text":"and we started a participatory design process,"},{"time":161193,"text":"and testing what was \navailable there in the market."},{"time":164840,"text":"Detached houses,"},{"time":166538,"text":"30 families could be accommodated."},{"time":169494,"text":"Row houses, 60 families."},{"time":173456,"text":"[\"100 families\"]\nThe only way to accommodate all of them"},{"time":176598,"text":"was by building in height,"},{"time":178920,"text":"and they threatened us"},{"time":180552,"text":"to go on a hunger strike"},{"time":182860,"text":"if we even dared to offer this"},{"time":185158,"text":"as a solution,"},{"time":186584,"text":"because they could not \nmake the tiny apartments"},{"time":189655,"text":"expand."},{"time":191109,"text":"So the conclusion with the families —"},{"time":193798,"text":"and this is important, \nnot our conclusion —"},{"time":195676,"text":"with the families, was that we had a problem."},{"time":198207,"text":"We had to innovate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199945,"text":"So what did we do?"},{"time":203720,"text":"Well, a middle-class family"},{"time":207619,"text":"lives reasonably well"},{"time":210499,"text":"in around 80 square meters,"},{"time":212850,"text":"but when there's no money,"},{"time":214522,"text":"what the market does"},{"time":215864,"text":"is to reduce the size of the house"},{"time":220122,"text":"to 40 square meters."},{"time":222971,"text":"What we said was,"},{"time":224719,"text":"what if,"},{"time":228845,"text":"instead of thinking of 40 square meters"},{"time":233378,"text":"as a small house,"},{"time":236059,"text":"why don't we consider it"},{"time":238385,"text":"half of a good one?"},{"time":241191,"text":"When you rephrase the problem"},{"time":242958,"text":"as half of a good house"},{"time":245664,"text":"instead of a small one,"},{"time":247299,"text":"the key question is, which half do we do?"},{"time":250508,"text":"And we thought we had \nto do with public money"},{"time":253210,"text":"the half that families won't \nbe able to do individually."},{"time":258619,"text":"We identified five design conditions"},{"time":261147,"text":"that belonged to the hard half of a house,"},{"time":263505,"text":"and we went back to the \nfamilies to do two things:"},{"time":266601,"text":"join forces and split tasks."},{"time":270600,"text":"Our design was something in between"},{"time":273584,"text":"a building and a house."},{"time":276265,"text":"As a building, it could pay"},{"time":278357,"text":"for expensive, well-located land,"},{"time":281349,"text":"and as a house, it could expand."},{"time":284970,"text":"If, in the process of not being expelled"},{"time":287554,"text":"to the periphery while getting a house,"},{"time":289920,"text":"families kept their \nnetwork and their jobs,"},{"time":292733,"text":"we knew that the expansion \nwould begin right away."},{"time":296980,"text":"So we went from this initial social housing"},{"time":301536,"text":"to a middle-class unit achieved\nby families themselves"},{"time":305930,"text":"within a couple of weeks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308666,"text":"This was our first project"},{"time":310439,"text":"in Iquique 10 years ago."},{"time":312766,"text":"This is our last project in Chile."},{"time":316243,"text":"Different designs, same principle:"},{"time":319194,"text":"You provide the frame,"},{"time":320760,"text":"and from then on, families take over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324598,"text":"So the purpose of design,"},{"time":328698,"text":"trying to understand and \ntrying to give an answer"},{"time":331708,"text":"to the \"3S\" menace,"},{"time":333360,"text":"scale, speed, and scarcity,"},{"time":334826,"text":"is to channel people's own building capacity."},{"time":338309,"text":"We won't solve the one million\npeople per week equation"},{"time":342714,"text":"unless we use people's own power for building."},{"time":347399,"text":"So, with the right design,"},{"time":349634,"text":"slums and favelas may not be the problem"},{"time":353035,"text":"but actually the only possible solution."},{"time":356784,"text":"The second case is how design can contribute"},{"time":359819,"text":"to sustainability."},{"time":361871,"text":"In 2012, we entered the competition"},{"time":364264,"text":"for the Angelini Innovation Center,"},{"time":366830,"text":"and the aim was to build"},{"time":368842,"text":"the right environment for knowledge creation."},{"time":373176,"text":"It is accepted that for such an aim,"},{"time":375660,"text":"knowledge creation,"},{"time":377196,"text":"interaction among people, \nface-to-face contact,"},{"time":379783,"text":"it's important, and we agreed on that."},{"time":381980,"text":"But for us, the question \nof the right environment"},{"time":385556,"text":"was a very literal question."},{"time":387722,"text":"We wanted to have a working space"},{"time":389842,"text":"with the right light, with the right temperature,"},{"time":392595,"text":"with the right air."},{"time":394477,"text":"So we asked ourselves:"},{"time":396555,"text":"Does the typical office building"},{"time":399145,"text":"help us in that sense?"},{"time":401256,"text":"Well, how does that \nbuilding look, typically?"},{"time":404870,"text":"It's a collection of floors,"},{"time":407454,"text":"one on top of each other,"},{"time":409361,"text":"with a core in the center"},{"time":412401,"text":"with elevators, stairs, \npipes, wires, everything,"},{"time":417090,"text":"and then a glass skin on the outside"},{"time":420677,"text":"that, due to direct sun radiation,"},{"time":424553,"text":"creates a huge greenhouse effect inside."},{"time":429761,"text":"In addition to that, let's say a guy"},{"time":431695,"text":"working on the seventh floor"},{"time":433431,"text":"goes every single day \nthrough the third floor,"},{"time":436142,"text":"but has no idea what the guy on that floor"},{"time":439180,"text":"is working on."},{"time":440909,"text":"So we thought, well, maybe \nwe have to turn this scheme"},{"time":444305,"text":"inside out."},{"time":446106,"text":"And what we did was,"},{"time":447928,"text":"let's have an open atrium,"},{"time":452110,"text":"a hollowed core,"},{"time":453999,"text":"the same collection of floors,"},{"time":455613,"text":"but have the walls and the mass in the perimeter,"},{"time":460053,"text":"so that when the sun hits,"},{"time":464317,"text":"it's not impacting directly glass, but a wall."},{"time":470444,"text":"When you have an open atrium inside,"},{"time":473181,"text":"you are able to see what others are doing"},{"time":475330,"text":"from within the building, and you have"},{"time":477181,"text":"a better way to control light,"},{"time":479380,"text":"and when you place the mass and the walls"},{"time":482783,"text":"in the perimeter,"},{"time":484439,"text":"then you are preventing direct sun radiation."},{"time":487872,"text":"You may also open those windows"},{"time":489792,"text":"and get cross-ventilation."},{"time":492688,"text":"We just made those openings"},{"time":495623,"text":"of such a scale that they could work"},{"time":497715,"text":"as elevated squares,"},{"time":499728,"text":"outdoor spaces throughout"},{"time":501472,"text":"the entire height of the building."},{"time":505135,"text":"None of this is rocket science."},{"time":506984,"text":"You don't require sophisticated programming."},{"time":509683,"text":"It's not about technology."},{"time":511416,"text":"This is just archaic, \nprimitive common sense,"},{"time":516838,"text":"and by using common sense,"},{"time":518806,"text":"we went from 120 kilowatts"},{"time":521787,"text":"per square meter per year,"},{"time":524127,"text":"which is the typical energy consumption"},{"time":526298,"text":"for cooling a glass tower,"},{"time":528290,"text":"to 40 kilowatts per square meter per year."},{"time":532620,"text":"So with the right design,"},{"time":534897,"text":"sustainability is nothing but the rigorous use"},{"time":537441,"text":"of common sense."},{"time":541174,"text":"Last case I would like \nto share is how design"},{"time":544147,"text":"can provide more comprehensive answers"},{"time":546442,"text":"against natural disasters."},{"time":548830,"text":"You may know that Chile, in 2010,"},{"time":551895,"text":"was hit by an 8.8 Richter scale"},{"time":555700,"text":"earthquake and tsunami,"},{"time":557823,"text":"and we were called to work"},{"time":559698,"text":"in the reconstruction of the Constitución,"},{"time":561940,"text":"in the southern part of the country."},{"time":563850,"text":"We were given 100 days, three months,"},{"time":567347,"text":"to design almost everything,"},{"time":569263,"text":"from public buildings to public space,"},{"time":571580,"text":"street grid, transportation, housing,"},{"time":573670,"text":"and mainly how to protect the city"},{"time":576424,"text":"against future tsunamis."},{"time":578679,"text":"This was new in Chilean urban design,"},{"time":581829,"text":"and there were in the \nair a couple of alternatives."},{"time":585202,"text":"First one:"},{"time":586454,"text":"Forbid installation on ground zero."},{"time":589103,"text":"Thirty million dollars spent mainly"},{"time":591140,"text":"in land expropriation."},{"time":593524,"text":"This is exactly what's being\ndiscussed in Japan nowadays,"},{"time":596786,"text":"and if you have a disciplined population"},{"time":598833,"text":"like the Japanese, this may work,"},{"time":601173,"text":"but we know that in Chile,"},{"time":602658,"text":"this land is going to be \noccupied illegally anyhow,"},{"time":606471,"text":"so this alternative was \nunrealistic and undesirable."},{"time":610543,"text":"Second alternative: build a big wall,"},{"time":613936,"text":"heavy infrastructure to resist"},{"time":616253,"text":"the energy of the waves."},{"time":618195,"text":"This alternative was conveniently lobbied"},{"time":620314,"text":"by big building companies,"},{"time":621675,"text":"because it meant 42 million \ndollars in contracts,"},{"time":625882,"text":"and was also politically preferred,"},{"time":628235,"text":"because it required no land expropriation."},{"time":632227,"text":"But Japan proved that trying to resist"},{"time":634977,"text":"the force of nature is useless."},{"time":638290,"text":"So this alternative was irresponsible."},{"time":641653,"text":"As in the housing process,"},{"time":643747,"text":"we had to include the community"},{"time":645624,"text":"in the way of finding a solution for this,"},{"time":648972,"text":"and we started a participatory design process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":652145,"text":"(Video) [In Spanish] Loudspeaker:\nWhat kind of city do you want?"},{"time":654416,"text":"Vote for Constitución."},{"time":655958,"text":"Go to the Open House and express your options."},{"time":658263,"text":"Participate!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":660436,"text":"Fisherman: I am a fisherman."},{"time":662510,"text":"Twenty-five fishermen work for me."},{"time":664619,"text":"Where should I take them? To the forest?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666958,"text":"Man: So why can't we have a concrete defense?"},{"time":670343,"text":"Done well, of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":672251,"text":"Man 2: I am the history of Constitución."},{"time":674141,"text":"And you come here to tell me\nthat I cannot keep on living here?"},{"time":678101,"text":"My whole family has lived here,"},{"time":680299,"text":"I raised my children here,"},{"time":681771,"text":"and my children will also \nraise their children here."},{"time":683856,"text":"and my grandchildren \nand everyone else will."},{"time":686364,"text":"But why are you imposing this on me?"},{"time":688890,"text":"You! You are imposing this on me!"},{"time":690767,"text":"In danger zone I am not authorized to build."},{"time":692558,"text":"He himself is saying that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694145,"text":"Man 3: No, no, no, Nieves..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":698940,"text":"Alejandro Aravena: I don't know if you were able"},{"time":701228,"text":"to read the subtitles, but you can tell"},{"time":703513,"text":"from the body language"},{"time":705157,"text":"that participatory design"},{"time":706435,"text":"is not a hippie, romantic,"},{"time":708759,"text":"let's-all-dream-together-about-\nthe-future-of-the-city"},{"time":712010,"text":"kind of thing."},{"time":714077,"text":"It is actually — (Applause)"},{"time":717570,"text":"It is actually not even with the families"},{"time":719970,"text":"trying to find the right answer."},{"time":723016,"text":"It is mainly trying to identify with precision"},{"time":725829,"text":"what is the right question."},{"time":727900,"text":"There is nothing worse than answering well"},{"time":729987,"text":"the wrong question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732091,"text":"So it was pretty obvious after this process"},{"time":735410,"text":"that, well, we chicken out here"},{"time":738941,"text":"and go away because it's too tense,"},{"time":741517,"text":"or we go even further in asking,"},{"time":743543,"text":"what else is bothering you?"},{"time":744938,"text":"What other problems do you have"},{"time":746691,"text":"and you want us to take \ncare of now that the city"},{"time":749273,"text":"will have to be rethought from scratch?"},{"time":753595,"text":"And what they said was,"},{"time":755791,"text":"look, fine to protect the city \nagainst future tsunamis,"},{"time":758577,"text":"we really appreciate, but the next one \nis going to come in, what, 20 years?"},{"time":763334,"text":"But every single year, we have problems"},{"time":765427,"text":"of flooding due to rain."},{"time":768290,"text":"In addition, we are in the middle"},{"time":770490,"text":"of the forest region of the country,"},{"time":772289,"text":"and our public space sucks."},{"time":775109,"text":"It's poor and it's scarce."},{"time":778900,"text":"And the origin of the city, our identity,"},{"time":781484,"text":"is not really connected to the buildings that fell,"},{"time":784370,"text":"it is connected to the river,"},{"time":785984,"text":"but the river cannot be accessed publicly,"},{"time":788798,"text":"because its shores are privately owned."},{"time":792500,"text":"So we thought that we had\nto produce a third alternative,"},{"time":797303,"text":"and our approach was \nagainst geographical threats,"},{"time":801847,"text":"have geographical answers."},{"time":805467,"text":"What if, in between the city"},{"time":811600,"text":"and the sea"},{"time":816590,"text":"we have a forest,"},{"time":819768,"text":"a forest that doesn't try to resist"},{"time":822354,"text":"the energy of nature,"},{"time":824212,"text":"but dissipates it by introducing friction?"},{"time":828271,"text":"A forest that may be able to laminate the water"},{"time":832164,"text":"and prevent the flooding?"},{"time":834515,"text":"That may pay the historical debt of public space,"},{"time":839599,"text":"and that may provide, finally,"},{"time":842242,"text":"democratic access to the river."},{"time":844660,"text":"So as a conclusion of the participatory design,"},{"time":847601,"text":"the alternative was validated politically and socially,"},{"time":850604,"text":"but there was still the problem of the cost:"},{"time":853715,"text":"48 million dollars."},{"time":856919,"text":"So what we did was a survey"},{"time":859323,"text":"in the public investment system,"},{"time":861875,"text":"and found out that there \nwere three ministries"},{"time":864190,"text":"with three projects in \nthe exact same place,"},{"time":867333,"text":"not knowing of the existence \nof the other projects."},{"time":870297,"text":"The sum of them: 52 million dollars."},{"time":874634,"text":"So design's power of synthesis"},{"time":877310,"text":"is trying to make a more efficient use"},{"time":879426,"text":"of the scarcest resource in cities,"},{"time":882283,"text":"which is not money but coordination."},{"time":885696,"text":"By doing so, we were able to save"},{"time":888478,"text":"four million dollars, and \nthat is why the forest"},{"time":891320,"text":"is today under construction."},{"time":894900,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":897516,"text":"So be it the force of self construction,"},{"time":901140,"text":"the force of common sense,"},{"time":904245,"text":"or the force of nature, all these forces"},{"time":907350,"text":"need to be translated into form,"},{"time":910781,"text":"and what that form is modeling and shaping"},{"time":914447,"text":"is not cement, bricks, or wood."},{"time":917677,"text":"It is life itself."},{"time":919922,"text":"Design's power of synthesis"},{"time":922260,"text":"is just an attempt to put"},{"time":924680,"text":"at the innermost core of architecture"},{"time":928312,"text":"the force of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":930180,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932969,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}